OL,3,CMan arrested after triple murder in
OL,4,CHertfordshire
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a triple
OL,7,Fmurder in Bushey, Hertfordshire.
OL,9,FKyle Clifford, 26, from Enfield, was
OL,10,Farrested on Thursday evening on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of three counts of murder.
OL,13,FHe remains in a serious condition in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday night, Hertfordshire Police
OL,17,Fwere called to a home in Ashlyn Close,
OL,18,FBushey, where three women were found
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries just after 7pm.
