OL,3,CMan arrested after triple murder in
OL,4,CHertfordshire
OL,6,FTributes have poured in for the
OL,7,Fvictims from neighbours and friends,
OL,8,Fwho described them as a "lovely
OL,9,Ffamily".
OL,11,FOn Thursday people crowded into St
OL,12,FJames' Church in Bushey, to pay their
OL,13,Frespect at a vigil held for the three
OL,14,Fwomen.
OL,16,FChildhood friend of Carol Hunt, Lea
OL,17,FHolloway, 60, said she had known Mrs
OL,18,FHunt since she was 16.
