OL,3,CMan arrested after triple murder in
OL,4,CHertfordshire
OL,6,FSpeaking outside St James' Church, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "We grew up together and were
OL,8,Fpregnant at the same time. This is the
OL,9,Fstuff nightmares are made of.
OL,11,F"I was there the night she met John
OL,12,F(Hunt). It was in a nightclub in Hemel
OL,13,FHempstead. We went out together, went
OL,14,Fto birthdays and events.
OL,16,F"It's very difficult. She was the
OL,17,Fnicest, kindest, sweetest person you
OL,18,Fcould ever meet. A beautiful person."
